result:
.grd-row-col-3-6
  table.p1
    tr
      th amount of trades
      td {{ report.trades }}
    tr
      th sharpe ratio
      td {{ round2(report.sharpe) }}
    tr
      th start balance
      td {{ round(report.startBalance) }} {{ report.currency }}
    tr
      th final balance
      td {{ round(report.balance) }} {{ report.currency }}
    tr
      th simulated profit

  .big.txt--right.price(:class='profitClass') {{ round(report.relativeProfit) }}%
